<text><img border="0" src="http://www.gsarchives.net/snes/front_mission/sprites/non-animated/portraits/ryuji_sakata.gif" alt="Ryuji" title="What am I, some kind of fashion model?" align="left"> <a href="http://www.gsarchives.net/index2.php?category=all&system=snes&game=front_mission&type=sprites&level0=non-animated">Here's</a> around seventeen portraits from the original Front Mission. If you're thinking the character designs look somewhat familiar, then that's because they were done by none other than Yoshitaka Amano, of Final Fantasy fame. I've always thought his designs were a bit odd, and that style is seen quite clearly in these portraits. Enjoy.</text>
